The port city of «Nagoya» is full of people who want to catch a great catch, and now you're one of them. Hoping that the goddess of fortune will send you a bigger catch, you go fishing, but even the most experienced can never know how well it will go.

You return with a smile on your face and proudly show off {0} to the people of the town. {1}. It's something to be proud of, I know, but there are still plenty of fish in these waters, so come back for another catch soon!
